Vodafone CEO Signals Interest in European Acquisitions, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-18T01:15:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/vodafone-ceo-signals-interest-in-european-acquisitions-ft-says.html
Vodafone Group Plc (VOD)  Chief Executive
Officer Vittorio Colao said the mobile-phone company is
interested in acquiring competitors in its European markets, the
Financial Times reported, citing comments by Colao yesterday.  Vodafone is prepared to be an “active” participant in
consolidation in  Europe , Colao said, according to the FT.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 